{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Velocity2015Review","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6942cce2-d77b-5252-afe6-24d6718cd9ef","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>参加了日前在京举办的 Velocity 技术大会，整理下主要内容做个记录，总结＋截图，给团队的小伙伴们分享的，同时这里发一份。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"总体感想\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E6%84%9F%E6%83%B3\" aria-label=\"总体感想 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>总体感想</h2>\n<p>性能优化开始从前后端代码／技术栈方面，全转向了距离硬件更近的领域（运维），比如：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTTP2/SPDY（TCP）</li>\n<li>DNS lookup</li>\n<li>CDN</li>\n<li>各种方法降低Latency / TTFB</li>\n</ul>\n<p>又比如，更贴近客户体验端的优化，比如：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Loading 中启用动画</li>\n<li>Page Block级别的Placeholder</li>\n</ul>\n<p>对于JS库的态度：众多的jQuery及其插件真的有用么？不如考虑使用原生JS+Polyfill</p>\n<p>Amazon还在支持IE6 ：给IE6用户非华丽的体验，实际是对用户也是好的<em>（这点很有深意，请细心体会，当然产品经理们更需要细心体会）</em></p>\n<p>作为前端，本次大会，新的技术点很少，Relay算一个，但只是提了一句，毕竟刚刚开源</p>\n<h2 id=\"参与制定w3c标准\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9Aw3c%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86\" aria-label=\"参与制定w3c标准 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参与制定W3C标准</h2>\n<p>未标准（未来）贡献你的微薄之力，有什么好点子尽量拿出来讨论。参与标准定制原则：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>毋以善小而不为</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"urls\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#urls\" aria-label=\"urls permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>URLs</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://discourse.wicg.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Specifiction Discourse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://extensiblewebmanifesto.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">The Extensible Web Manifesto</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/community/wicg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">WEB PLATFORM INCUBATOR COMMUNITY GROUP</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://webcomponents.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">webcomponents</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://testthewebforward.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Test the Web Forward</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"yahoo的reactflux在s／c端的实践\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#yahoo%E7%9A%84reactflux%E5%9C%A8s%EF%BC%8Fc%E7%AB%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5\" aria-label=\"yahoo的reactflux在s／c端的实践 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Yahoo的React&#x26;Flux在S／C端的实践</h2>\n<h3 id=\"模型\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"模型 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>模型</h3>\n<p>Server side: Node.js + Express</p>\n<p>Client side: Webpack + Polyfills</p>\n<p>Middle area: Fluxible + React + CommonJS</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1848.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"目前已经实装该架构的站点\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E5%AE%9E%E8%A3%85%E8%AF%A5%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9\" aria-label=\"目前已经实装该架构的站点 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>目前已经实装该架构的站点</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Yahoo台湾M站</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://sports.yahoo.com/dailyfantasy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sports Daily Fantasy App</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/beauty\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Beauty digital magazines</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"技术点\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%82%B9\" aria-label=\"技术点 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>技术点</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Flux实现，使用<a href=\"http://fluxible.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">fluxible</a></li>\n<li>\n<p>YUI团队开源的（也许有用的）React组件</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/yahoo/react-i13n\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">react i13n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/yahoo/react-intl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">react intl</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"前端性能-alva-cheung-google\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD-alva-cheung-google\" aria-label=\"前端性能 alva cheung google permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前端性能 Alva Cheung (Google)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"要点：\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A6%81%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A\" aria-label=\"要点： permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>要点：</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>数据显示：页面加载时间会随着带宽增加越来越不明显；但会跟随Latency的降低而持续减低 <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1859.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>使用DNS Prefetch</li>\n<li>谨慎使用 Prerender，<strong>举例：google结果页的前两个结果会启用prerender，给用户造成结果秒开的体验</strong></li>\n<li>\n<p>Javascript中的代码细节：<img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1860.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Dog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dog1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Dog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Jim'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dog2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Dog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Bin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// dog1和dog2公用一个hidden class</span>\n\ndog2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>breed <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'new name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//此时内存中会新创建hidden class一个</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Javascript中的代码细节：compiler（特制closure compiler，参考<a href=\"https://developers.google.com/closure/compiler/docs/js-for-compiler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">这里</a>和<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zj831007/article/details/6801110\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">这里是中文的</a>）会认识JS原文件中的注解(annotation)，有针对性的进行优化<strong>（这是新知识点）</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * Returns a new Point which is the original point translated by distance in\n * both the x and y dimensions.\n * @param {example.Point} point\n * @param {number} distance\n * @return {example.Point}\n */</span>\nexample<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">translate</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">point<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> distance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    x<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> point<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> distance<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    y<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> point<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>y <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> distance\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>在真实的设备上测试FPS。（Timeline工具的使用）<img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1861.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>事件节流技术（老生常谈的 throttling）<img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1862.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"功能实验模型\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"功能实验模型 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>功能实验模型</h2>\n<p>如何在真实环境上测试N个功能？看每个新功能的实际效果。<img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1871.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"代码方案：\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9A\" aria-label=\"代码方案： permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>代码方案：</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>在JS中if（功能开关）；在SCSS中if（功能开关）<img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1872.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>在JS中原型链覆盖；在SCSS中class覆盖<img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1873.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"资源方案：\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9A\" aria-label=\"资源方案： permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>资源方案：</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>独立：NONONONONO <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1874.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>HTTP2的Server Push <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1875.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>不变的＋可变的combo <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1876.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"yahoo-react--flux-实践\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#yahoo-react--flux-%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5\" aria-label=\"yahoo react  flux 实践 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Yahoo React &#x26; Flux 实践</h2>\n<p>开场大量篇幅讲了React基础和Flux概念</p>\n<p>重要实践填坑内容，因为被叫出去说事，没听到……</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Flux方案的升级版本 <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1879.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>启用了Apache的ESI组件，进行页面拼装，降低TTFB <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1881.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>服务器React渲染的问题和技巧 <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1882.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>Flux下通过Store管理提炼数据 <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1885.JPG\" alt=\"图\"> (超注：我们广告这边动辄20M的JSON……噩梦）</li>\n<li>服务端渲染（传统站点） VS 客户端渲染（后市场M站） VS Preload（咱们有么……） 三种渲染方式对比，适应场景 <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1887.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>如果你用了lodash&#x26;&#x26;lodash.merge，记得一定要<code class=\"language-text\">require(&#39;lodash/object/merge&#39;)</code><strong>性能巨坑</strong> <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1888.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>CSS的处理，在用<a href=\"http://acss.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Atomic CSS\n</a></li>\n<li>中检测要做S／C端的区别，比如：服务器端的那接口用<code class=\"language-text\">request</code>，客户端要封装一层<code class=\"language-text\">ajax</code>，统一对外暴露一套API供组件使用</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"淘宝天猫m\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%B7%98%E5%AE%9D%E5%A4%A9%E7%8C%ABm\" aria-label=\"淘宝天猫m permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>淘宝天猫M</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>使用CDN！阿里云有强大的CDN！</li>\n<li>在移动端，连接数代价远远高于代码量（file size）</li>\n<li>前端能做的：域名收敛（降低其他域名出现的次数）</li>\n<li>淘宝首页用one-request打包，听着类似于Webpack，Webpack未来两周内，准备好会给大家分享</li>\n<li>自己写Scroll，因为ios safari 原生 scroll触发问题，不能在其中做任何操作</li>\n<li>降低<code class=\"language-text\">composition layers</code>，提升FPS，会产生<code class=\"language-text\">composition layers</code>的方法 <img src=\"http://dl.caichao.me/assets/velocity2015/IMG_1894.JPG\" alt=\"图\"></li>\n<li>对图片的处理，50质量压缩＋150%的锐化（CDN自动完成）</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Velocity2015Review","tagSlugs":["/tag/技术大会/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2015-08-18","description":"参加了日前在京举办的 Velocity 技术大会，整理下主要内容做个记录。","tags":["技术大会"],"title":"Velocity 2015 Review","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Velocity2015Review"}}}